<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>FckHome</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: #f4f7fb;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    /* Navbar */
    #navbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      gap: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4CAF50, #2E7D32);
      color: white;
      width: 100%;
      height: 56px;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }

    #navbar a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
    }

    #navbar a:hover {
      color: #ffeb3b;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    #hero {
      background: url('/assets/hero-bg.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background-color: #2E7D32; /* fallback if image missing */
    }

    #hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    #hero p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* About Section */
    #about {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    #about h2 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #2E7D32;
    }

    #about p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #555;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      background: #2E7D32;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section id="hero">
    <h1>Welcome to FckHome</h1>
    <p>Where comfort meets affordability. Explore homes that fit your lifestyle, curated with care.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p><strong>FckHome</strong> is a project proudly created by <strong>Rohit Singh</strong>.</p>
    <p>Our mission is simple: to provide an easy way to find and showcase homes that people can truly call their own. Whether you're buying, renting, or just exploring, we make the experience smooth and enjoyable.</p>
    <p>Started as a personal initiative, <strong>FckHome</strong> blends technology, design, and reliability into one platform that connects people with their dream spaces.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> FckHome | Built with ❤️ by Rohit Singh</p>
    <p>Contact: support@justhome.com</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
